JWKsD\"\u003e这不是拜金主义，这是残酷的现实..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"96hNx_eM\"\u003e“残酷的现实已直逼心理防线..”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"KZWj68TY\"\u003e翻出“过时”的电视剧《马大帅》看看马大帅是怎么活着的，哭丧、卖艺、挨揍，为的无非是“挣俩钱儿”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"KySD35ve\"\u003e唯有碎银几两，可解世上慌张..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"tUgPVA5K\"\u003e职场焦虑的根源，其实就是“出力不挣钱”，在这个基础上，还看着同事、领导“哐哐吃，库库捞”，在不就是““l二代”们各种阶级碾压，一对比，“红眼病”犯了，又找不到机会镶在既得利益链上，自己家庭这块儿，又是各种支出，若X生活再不得劲儿，就会既痛苦又着急..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Xljs9vzy\"\u003e痛苦+着急+支出+（- X）=焦虑..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"CqGe4Yum\"\u003e赌场不得志，情场失意，Debuff拉满，可不焦虑么..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"8HPhuZYl\"\u003e破局办法就是：“什么都别想，一切向钱看”..\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"GmxdzgT3\"\u003e献祭你觉得你可以献祭的；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"6m7njeQe\"\u003e折现你觉得可以折现的；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"efg-V2E_\"\u003e别的不要瞎JB想，富起来再说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":12,"favorite_count":1,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1933804729961543373}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"47_1753853552.226","type":"feed","offset":47,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753853552,"updated_time":1753853552,"target":{"id":"1932518370869253812","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1932518370869253812","author":{"id":"2ddc134b2d6bcde89f883e4c051f1bc2","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/2ddc134b2d6bcde89f883e4c051f1bc2","user_type":"people","url_token":"ke-ke-neng-xing","name":"晏北","headline":"公众号——晏北，理解芯片，理解经济","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0874375d3926d8580eec8f4e8de3ce1_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"badge":[{"type":"best_answerer","description":"职场话题下的优秀答主","topic_names":["职场"],"topic_ids":[2566]},{"type":"super_activity","description":"知势榜职场领域成长力榜答主"}],"followers_count":6816,"is_following":false,